"Ibha yesikhala nokubhala ngamagama amakhulu kulungisa amaphutha amagama athayiphwe kabi"
"Idatha yakho evumelanisiwe izosuswa emafini. Ingabe uqinisekile?"

"Isichazamazwi sakho somuntu siqu sizovumelaniswa siphinde senziwe isipele kumaseva we-Google. Ulwazi lezibalo lemvamisa yegama lingaqoqwa ukusiza ukuthuthukisa imikhiqizo yethu. Ukuqoqwa nokusetshenziswa kwalo lonke ulwazi kuzohambisana ne-""Inqubomgomo Yobumfihlo ye-Google""."
"Vumelanisa isichazamazwi sakho kuwo wonke amadivayisi wakho"
"Ukuvumelanisa akutholakali kumadivayisi anezinhlelo zokusebenza ze-Google zama-akhawunti webhizinisi"
"Isitayela sakho sokufakwayo sokwenza ngokwezifiso sidinga ukunikwa amandla ngaphambi kokusisebenzisa. Ufuna ukusinika amandla manje?"
"Faka izikhala ngesikhathi sokuthinta ngokushelelela kukhiye wesikhala"
"Ukhiye wokushintsha ulimi ubandakanya ezinye izindlela zokungenayo"
"I-%s isivele inikwe amandla kulimi lwakho nakuzilungiselelo zokufaka, ngakho-ke lesi sinyathelo senziwe. Qhubekela kwesilandelayo!"
"Sicela uhlole i-\"%s\" kulimi lwakho nezilungiselelo zokokufaka. Lokhu kuzoyigunyaza ukuthi isebenze kudivayisi yakho."
"Okulandelayo, khetha i-\"%s\" njengendlela yakho yokufaka umbhalo osebenzayo."
"Manje usungathayipha ngokufaka zonke izinhlelo zokusebenza eziyizintandokazi zakho nge-%s."

"Ulimi olukhethiwe kudivayisi yakho yeselula lunesichazamazwi.
Sincoma ukuthi ulande isichazamazwi se-%1$s ukuze uthuthukise umuzwa wakho wokuthayipha.

Ukulanda kungathatha iminithi noma amabili nge-3G. Izindleko zingasebenza uma ungenalo icebo ledatha elingakhawulelwe.
Uma ungenasiqiniseko sokuthi iliphi icebo ledatha onalo, sincoma ukuthi uthole uxhumo lwe-Wi-Fi ukuze uqale ukulanda ngokuzenzakalela.

Ithiphu: Ungalanda futhi ususe izichazamazwi ngokuya kokuthi Izilimi nokufaka kumenyu izilungiselelo kudivayisi yakho yeselula."
